    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, chop your <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken breast portion[s] </strong>into strips</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a very large drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Add the <strong>chicken strips</strong> to a bowl with your <strong>cornflour</strong> and give it a good mix up until all the chicken is coated</p>",
