          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> sticky chilli sauce </strong>to the pan and cook for 3 min or until the sauce begins to thicken and the pepper has softened</p><p>Once thickened, add the<strong> crispy chicken </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min further until the chicken is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>sticky free range chicken</strong></p>",
