    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chips are cooked, add the<strong> remaining chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the tray and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>salt & pepper chips</strong></p>",
